# Aliro Lab profiling overlay: turns the transaction trace on
# (CONFIG_WOZ_ALIRO_LAB). Layered ONLY by `make lab-build` / `make lab-flash`,
# into an isolated build-lab/ tree — a normal `make build` never sees this file,
# so production images stay default-off. See tests/host/data/README.md.
CONFIG_WOZ_ALIRO_LAB=y
